      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-start-and-end-date" data-step-uuid="51d8d812-ef84-4f5d-a153-a3243ecca607">
    <h2 id="view-start-and-end-date" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Start and End Date</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/744/083/original/3cbb7508-b96d-4e64-ba32-9810b26ddf1c.png" srcset="" alt="View Start and End Date" height="457" width="600">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_22e3c936-b17a-4f85-bd16-003bedd64eb8" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To filter by start and end date, click the <strong>Start &amp; End Date</strong> option [1]. Then click in the <strong>Start Date</strong> and/or <strong>End Date</strong> fields and select dates [2]. Click the <strong>Apply</strong> button [3]. The Gradebook displays only assignments that have a due date at or beyond the start date and/or at or before the end date.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-filters" data-step-uuid="fb2a24ba-a009-4590-aa23-08ae1b7f28b3">
